data.title: Get A Sneak Peek At Weezer’s Setlist Tonight In Bangor
data.meta_description: Ready to rock? Weezer is in town to help out!
data.text:
Ready to rock? Weezer is in town to help out!

The iconic band, Weezer will bring their "Indie Rock Road Trip" tour to the Maine Savins Amphitheatre to Bangor tonight at 7pm, featuring special guests, Modest Mouse, Future Islands, Spoon, Momma, Joyce Manor, and White Reaper.

Weezer have sold 10 million albums in the US and over 35 million worldwide. They also have a truckoad of classic hits that they are ready to bring to the Bangor Waterfront tonight.

On the weather front for tonight, finally we have some great news! There is no threat of rain in the forecast, and the temps looks warm and comfy throughout the evening.
